50	 *
51	 * ── Anchoring + negation (C-009/C-019/C-059, ported idea from corpus-index.js) ───────────────────
52	 * Every derived pattern is word-boundary anchored on every token; a bare prefix/substring is
53	 * unrepresentable and REJECTED by validateSpec (the "cost"->pricing, /^EU/->EUROPEAN class). Prohibition
